data.description: Solar for electric savings!!!(OWNED)3/2/1 Pool home with four car carport with an amazing two story workshop!! This block home is centrally located between Lake Griffin and Lake Harris part of Lake county's highly sought after chain of lakes.   As you enter the home you can't help but notice the great picture window overlooking the wonderfully canopied tree.  An extra wide walkway and sweet front porch.  The home has had updating including laminate flooring, granite countertops in the kitchen, real wood cabinets with soft close drawers and tile backsplash, a breakfast bar and custom lighting and a pass through window for added convenience.  There's a generously shared dining and living room space which includes a rock wall and overlooks the spacious backyard and pool area.  Home also has a lanai. The huge back yard houses the carport and workshop.  Tons of space to make your own man cave or house a favorite hobby.  The main house has many upgrades including a jetted bathtub in the hall bath with a vessel sink. The main bedroom has a back door for easy access to the pool, a walk in shower with a pebble floor and vessel sink!   Sleepy Hollow Recreational Center is just minutes away to enjoy sports, playgrounds and picnic areas. Tons of shopping, restaurants and recreation all nearby. Home is 15 minutes south of the villages and about one hour north of Orlando.
